Some tips: Target sells Ghiardelli 60% cacao chips in a 11.5 ounce bag for only $2.50. This is almost all of the chocolate you need for this recipe. I accidently spent 3 times this much for the same amt of chocolate at the grocery. Target also sells the espresso powder. I didn't have a 10X15 in. pan so I used two 9 inch cake pans. The total area is just slightly larger than that of the other pan so I decreased baking times very slightly (like a minute or two. The meringue was more than finished in 1 hour total. Save the extra two whites in the cake layer for the meringue for less waste. I don't have a sifter and just rubbed the cocoa over the souffle layers which turned out fine.

