To susankatz from Armonk. A word of caution. If you switch from hazelnuts to pecans as you said you wanted to do, be careful as pecans are much more oily than hazelnuts and may ruin the meringue. If you don't like hazelnuts a better alternative would be almonds, not as oily as pecans.

